# API Tests for Contacts API

### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single contact by ID (replace <ID> with actual contact ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/<ID>
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
  "birthday": "1990-01-01"
}

###

### Update a contact by ID (replace <ID> with actual contact ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/users/<ID>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "janesmith@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Green",
  "birthday": "1985-05-15"
}

###

### Delete a contact by ID (replace <ID> with actual contact ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/<ID>

